The navy is a naval battle in the terminal. But the two players communicates by signals
between two process.

The two players are on the smae computer but on diferents terminals. thay have input files
that are the position of their boats.

The frist player lauch the game like this ./navy input_file. The program show his
PID, so the second player lauch the game like that ./navy enemy_PID input_file

And then the two player can play, programs comunicates by signals.

You can find input_file in the map folder
